{"name":"problem","description":"Records problems identified within the IT environment, aimed at root cause analysis and resolution to prevent future incidents.","summary":"In the context of ServiceNow, the \"problem\" object is a key component of the IT Service Management (ITSM) module, specifically within the Problem Management process. Here's a summary of the \"problem\" object:\n\n### Summary of the \"Problem\" Object in ServiceNow\n\n1. **Purpose**:\n   - The \"problem\" object is designed to identify, analyze, and resolve the root causes of incidents to prevent them from recurring.\n\n2. **Key Attributes**:\n   - **Problem ID**: A unique identifier for each problem record.\n   - **Short Description**: A brief summary of the problem.\n   - **Description**: A detailed explanation of the problem.\n   - **State**: The current status of the problem (e.g., New, In Progress, Resolved, Closed).\n   - **Priority**: The importance and urgency of the problem.\n   - **Assigned To**: The individual or group responsible for resolving the problem.\n   - **Category**: The type or classification of the problem.\n   - **Impact**: The effect of the problem on the business or service.\n   - **Urgency**: The importance of resolving the problem quickly.\n   - **Work Notes**: Internal notes and updates related to the problem.\n   - **Resolution Information**: Details about how the problem was resolved.\n\n3. **Related Objects**:\n   - **Incidents**: Problems can be linked to multiple incidents to track the impact and resolution progress.\n   - **Changes**: Problems may require changes to be implemented as part of the resolution process.\n   - **Knowledge Articles**: Problems can be linked to knowledge articles to document solutions and best practices.\n\n4. **Workflow**:\n   - **Identification**: Recognizing that a problem exists, often through recurring incidents.\n   - **Analysis**: Investigating the root cause of the problem.\n   - **Resolution**: Implementing a solution to address the root cause.\n   - **Closure**: Documenting the resolution and ensuring that the problem is fully addressed.\n\n5. **Benefits**:\n   - **Proactive Management**: Helps in identifying and resolving issues before they cause major disruptions.\n   - **Improved Service Quality**: Reduces the frequency of incidents","attributes":[{"name":"parent","type":"reference"},{"name":"watch_list","type":"glide_list"},{"name":"fix_communicated_by","type":"reference"},{"name":"upon_reject","type":"string"},{"name":"sys_updated_on","type":"glide_date_time"},{"name":"approval_history","type":"journal"},{"name":"skills","type":"glide_list"},{"name":"number","type":"string"},{"name":"state","type":"integer"},{"name":"sys_created_by","type":"string"},{"name":"knowledge","type":"boolean"},{"name":"order","type":"integer"},{"name":"major_problem","type":"boolean"},{"name":"cmdb_ci","type":"reference"},{"name":"delivery_plan","type":"reference"},{"name":"impact","type":"integer"},{"name":"contract","type":"reference"},{"name":"active","type":"boolean"},{"name":"work_notes_list","type":"glide_list"},{"name":"priority","type":"integer"},{"name":"sys_domain_path","type":"domain_path"},{"name":"business_duration","type":"glide_duration"},{"name":"group_list","type":"glide_list"},{"name":"approval_set","type":"glide_date_time"},{"name":"universal_request","type":"reference"},{"name":"short_description","type":"string"},{"name":"correlation_display","type":"string"},{"name":"delivery_task","type":"reference"},{"name":"work_start","type":"glide_date_time"},{"name":"known_error","type":"boolean"},{"name":"additional_assignee_list","type":"glide_list"},{"name":"sys_class_name","type":"sys_class_name"},{"name":"service_offering","type":"reference"},{"name":"workaround","type":"html"},{"name":"closed_by","type":"reference"},{"name":"follow_up","type":"glide_date_time"},{"name":"reopened_by","type":"reference"},{"name":"reassignment_count","type":"integer"},{"name":"confirmed_at","type":"glide_dat